    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves level 2 against a required level of 3 due to single static loading condition; risk accepted given medium model influence, corroborating published data, and conservative acceptance bounds. Overall credibility sufficient for medium-assurance regulatory submission. Note: the material and geometry input dataset (vintage 2025-10-30) predates the model revision of 2026-02-14; re-validation with updated inputs is planned prior to the next design iteration submission.",
